name: Ape Dao Remix! #2
description:
APE DAO REMIX! Project is a collection of 5,550 NFTs derived from 
the first 50 BAYC NFTs that were the genesis of APE DAO. Each of
 the DAO's Apes was remixed by some of the hottest NFT artists in 
the community. There are 111 editions of each Remix in the collection
 and each NFT includes membership to the exclusive APE DAO community.
